Here are the motivations that kept us on track : 🫴 Easy to integrate for anyone (even on legacy systems)🦥 Useful : make people save time, ie. make more with less effort and install : for an improved Time to market for us and others, eg. create new business opportunities ideas : people should feel the desire to use the product and feel joy while using it🧑‍🤝‍🧑 Create new relationships with people and discover new practicesNext, we'll focus on  the benefits : ♾️ Continuous delivery tools and automation📼 New ways of documentation with next-gen tools (beacause it always matters) (because they're both a cool and efficient way to get things done)🧑‍🎨 Creative product design and developmentHopefully you'll like it as much as we do...and will engage yourself on the same kind of way : the  journey 🤗
